These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, red, lavender
1. the person who likes lavender is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Color   | azure | red | lavender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, jazz
1. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, baking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Hobby   | hiking | card-games | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, july
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | january | august | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Game   | poker | bridge | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, snooker
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Game   | bridge | backgammon | snooker |

