.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, badminton
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | lacrosse | soccer | badminton |

