.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, ship, jet-ski
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Transport   | ship | jet-ski | roller |

 #################################

 
